    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f0cea9a2-1896-42fd-9a67-2aa6431d35a8">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f0cea9a2-1896-42fd-9a67-2aa6431d35a8">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f0cea9a2-1896-42fd-9a67-2aa6431d35a8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-06-13/debates/4f77a1fb-21f7-42b3-9fc8-e59fa0dc7c54/SchumanPlan#contribution-f0cea9a2-1896-42fd-9a67-2aa6431d35a8">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">They have been kept fully informed all the time. The general practice in these matters has been stated over and over again. On matters of this kind Commonwealth Governments are kept fully informed. It is up to them, if they wish to make any statements or suggestions, to do so.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f0cea9a2-1896-42fd-9a67-2aa6431d35a8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-06-13/debates/4f77a1fb-21f7-42b3-9fc8-e59fa0dc7c54/SchumanPlan#contribution-f0cea9a2-1896-42fd-9a67-2aa6431d35a8">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-e7f5616b-af1c-4524-819b-84f150731224">
